Title: Restricts certain practices from remote supervision by licensed pharmacists
Summary: Prohibits drugs from being dispensed unless a licensed pharmacist has verified that: the package contains the drug to be dispensed, whether the drug is packaged in a child-resistant container, whether a stock container is open and the quantity of the drug to be dispensed.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law, in relation to restricting certain practices from remote supervision by licensed pharmacists
